data.description: Welcome to your move-in ready home with a spectacular in-law suite, located in the highly sought after neighborhood of Hamilton Mill. This home greets you with fresh exterior paint, professional landscaping, including an irrigation system and an amazing rocking chair front porch before you step inside to a vaulted foyer, formal dining room and your own flex/office area. Enjoy an open-concept living room and kitchen space with an island, plenty of storage, all new lighting and beautiful hardwoods throughout the entire first floor. Take in the gorgeous view of the private, wooded, flat backyard on your oversized deck spanning the entire home and wrapping around to a bonus screened area for additional privacy. Upstairs is a huge primary bedroom with tray ceilings and a generous walk-in closet. The renovated ensuite bathroom features a massive walk-in shower complete with multiple shower heads and a bench, dual sinks and plenty of cabinets for storage. Three spacious bedrooms with large closets, vaulted ceilings and plenty of natural light, a laundry room and another full bathroom round out the second floor. Make your way downstairs to your fully finished basement completely functional with its own separate entrance, a full sized living room, all new LVP flooring, two larger sized bedrooms with walk-in closets, a full bathroom and the cutest kitchen with full size appliances, centrally located for maximum use. A great space for an in-law suite, roommates or guests. The outside covered patio offers a hot tub for relaxing and entertaining and the back yard is fully fenced in with plenty of space to make it your own!! This home provides a private retreat yet conveniently located near 985, I-85, the Mall of Georgia, Little Mulberry Park, Duncan Creek Park, Bogan Park, Chateau Elan, Lake Lanier and the highly rated Mill Creek School District. Enjoy the various amenities of Hamilton Mill with pools, tennis, pickleball, volleyball, basketball, soccer, fishing, fitness center, walking track and planned neighborhood activities.
